[32m+[m[32m## ✨ Features[m
 [m
[31m-## Features[m
[32m+[m[32m- **AI Extraction:** Automatically extracts English-foreign word pairs from uploaded documents.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Robust Parsing:** Fail-safe JSON extraction that handles varied AI response formats.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Interactive Flashcards:** Digital cards with a sleek glassmorphism design.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Example Sentences:** AI-generated bilingual sentences for better context.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **MCQ Quizzes:** Interactive multiple-choice quizzes with intelligent distractor generation.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Quiz Review:** High-performance summary screen to review all answered questions.[m
[32m+[m[32m- **Privacy First:** Your API keys are stored only in your browser's local storage.[m
 [m
[31m-- 📄 **Multi-File Upload** — Upload multiple PDF, DOCX, or TXT files at once[m
[31m-- 🃏 **Flashcards** — Click-to-flip cards showing English on front, translation on back[m
[31m-- 📝 **Example Sentences** — AI-generated sentences showing each word in context[m
[31m-- ❓ **MCQ Quiz** — Multiple choice questions built from your uploaded words[m
[31m-- 💾 **Persistent Storage** — Words saved in browser localStorage, survive page refresh[m
[31m-- 🔄 **Merge Uploads** — New uploads add to existing words, nothing gets overwritten[m
[31m-- 🗑️ **Reset** — One button clears all stored data[m
[31m-- 📱 **Responsive** — Works on desktop and mobile[m
